{"body":"Fixes #56\n\n## Summary\n- Add `examples/universal-app`, a Vite React UI that imports `add` and `multiply` from the package source.\n- Add GitHub Pages, Electron Forge desktop, and Capacitor Android/iOS build paths with root convenience scripts.\n- Add a dedicated example workflow, case-study research data, Playwright screenshots, and a minor changeset.\n\n## Reproduction and verification\n- Reproduced the missing support first with `node --test --test-timeout=30000 tests/universal-app.test.js`; the failing pre-implementation log is committed under `docs/case-studies/issue-56/data/universal-app-test-before.log`.\n- `npm test`\n- `npm run check`\n- `npm run example:web:build`\n- `npm run example:desktop:package`\n- `npm run example:mobile:sync`\n- `bun test --timeout 30000`\n- `deno test --allow-read`\n- `bash scripts/check-mjs-syntax.sh`\n- `bash scripts/check-file-line-limits.sh`\n- `node scripts/validate-changeset.mjs`\n\n## Screenshots\n\nDesktop web render:\n\n![Universal app desktop render](https://github.com/link-foundation/js-ai-driven-development-pipeline-template/blob/issue-56-792944d0466b/docs/case-studies/issue-56/artifacts/universal-app-web.png?raw=true)\n\nMobile web render:\n\n![Universal app mobile render](https://github.com/link-foundation/js-ai-driven-development-pipeline-template/blob/issue-56-792944d0466b/docs/case-studies/issue-56/artifacts/universal-app-mobile.png?raw=true)\n\n## Notes\n- Android and iOS CI jobs are gated behind `EXAMPLE_APP_ENABLE_ANDROID_BUILD` and `EXAMPLE_APP_ENABLE_IOS_BUILD` repository variables so native projects and signing choices remain explicit.\n- The example pins Node-20-compatible Vite/Capacitor/Electron versions while the workflow itself uses the repository's current Node setup pattern.","commits":[{"authoredDate":"2026-05-12T10:47:39Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-05-12T10:47:39Z","messageBody":"Adding .gitk